highlights.text: “Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 169 days straight.
Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “luther (with sza)” is the highest at #16.
“CURSE (รักใครไม่เป็น)” by Z9, 2K, and Saran is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #5.
“Dimmi tu quando sei pronto per fare l'amore” by Vale LP and Lil Jolie is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 4 spots at #9.
